description: This file is an entry point for a React-based frontend application. It imports React libraries, CSS styling, and the main App component. It initializes the React application by rendering the App component into the DOM element with id 'root' using ReactDOM.createRoot.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for the React application in the specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React components into the created root.
